HEADWORD: Snod
<hw>Snod</hw> <pr>(sn⟦ocr⟧d)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Snood</er>.]</ety> <def>A fillet; a headband; a snood.</def>
<mark>[Obs. or Prov. Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

