==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Snod
<hw>Snod</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Scot. <ets>snod</ets> to prune, put
in order.]</ety> <def>Trimmed; smooth; neat; trim; sly; cunning;
demure.</def> <mark>[Prov. Eng. & Scot.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Snoff</ent>⟦br⟧
